    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Panel paintings installed in churches with religious texts appropriate to the the guild responsible for sponsoring the panel. These often have an ornamented frame bearing references to the guild itelf.</Note_Text>
